title: why havent i gotten my gold rewards yet
body: i ended this season in gold and i havnt gotten any rewards yet all my frinds have gotten their why havent i gotten mine ?

replies.body: Looks like your account had a 2-week suspension after 8/22, which would have disqualified you from the ranked rewards.

Did you check the eligibility requirements? Are you sure you are supposed to get them? If you are, you can submit a ticket to them.
Or wait to check if any rioter sees your thread and check your account.
